description: Tony Hunter makes his NK debut taking on NK veteran Sebastian Keys. With his "backyard-wrestling" experience Tony thinks he can kick some asses on NK. Getting caught in a full nelson and received some punches to his gut, Tony is going balls to the wall. Sebastian continues with his ass slapping and face sitting. He's relentless for sexual domination. Can Sebastian prove this new punk wrong? Or will Tony rise to the challenge?
title: Tony Hunter vs Sebastian Keys
